snippet.title: Gran Turismo 3 Trailer
snippet.description:
This is from the 2001 Demo Disc. Everyone who owned a PS2 has this demo disc.

This trailer is for Gran Turismo 3: A-Spec

Notes from Uploader:
One of the best Gran Turismo games ever made and this trailer is very good and memorable.
Featuring one of my favourite songs in the soundtrack, Feeder - Just A Day.
